    "headline": "EQT (EQT) Q1 2026 Earnings Call Transcript",
    "summary": "To put this into perspective, in just 90 days, we generated roughly as much free cash flow as we did during the entirety of 2022, a year when gas prices were over $6.  With leverage now below 1x net debt to EBITDA and our long-term $5 billion net debt target within reach by year-end, EQT has entered a new chapter, one defined by financial strength, durable free cash flow generation and sustainable growth.",
